 , and the final value of the investment,  ğ¹ğ‘‰
 , or  ROI=ğ¹ğ‘‰âˆ’ğ‘ƒğ‘ƒ
 , expressed as a percentage.
NOTE: The length of time of the investment is not considered in ROI.

